{"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbulletlist"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS"},{"introducedAt":"13.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS"},{"introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"tvOS"},{"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS"},{"introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"unavailable":false,"name":"watchOS"}],"roleHeading":"Structure","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSBulletListV","title":"OUDSBulletList","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSBulletList"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSBulletList"}],"symbolKind":"struct"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list is a UI element that helps to view in related individual text items grouped together; items usually starting with a number or a bullet."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list is also known as "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Unordered list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Ordered list","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and is not an interactive element by default."}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Structures","generated":true,"title":"Structures","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/Item"]},{"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true,"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/init(type:textStyle:isBold:items:)"]},{"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true,"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/body"]},{"anchor":"Type-Aliases","generated":true,"title":"Type Aliases","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/UnorderedIcon"]},{"anchor":"Enumerations","generated":true,"title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/TextStyle","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/Type","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/UnorderedAsset"]},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true,"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSBulletList\/View-Implementations"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"type":"conformsTo"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSBulletList","kind":"identifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/ContentDisplay"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Types","level":2,"text":"Types"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Three types are proposed:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unordered (by default)"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Collects related items that don’t need to be in a specific order or sequence."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Ordered"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Collects related items with numeric order or sequence."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bare"}]},{"type":"text","text":": An unordered list without any bullets or alphanumeric sequence."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Types can be mixed in list, but must be identical for the same ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSBulletList.NestedLevel","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Levels","level":2,"text":"Levels"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Lists can include nested items to indicate hierarchy or subcategories, with indentation distinguishing each level.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Arrange ordered list items logically, such as ranking by importance, highest to lowest values, or in alphabetical \/ numeric order.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Three levels are maximum.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Text-Style","level":2,"text":"Text Style"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"List can be used with different font sizes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Body Large"}]},{"type":"text","text":": If the text accompanying the list component is the Body Large text. This variant is designed for more visual, engaging experiences."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Body Medium"}]},{"type":"text","text":": If the text accompanying the list component is the Body Medium text. This variant is best suited for functional, task-oriented experiences."}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"it is not allowed to have a depth of items greater than 3"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Internationalisation-considerations","level":2,"text":"Internationalisation considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For latin-based speaking countries, like France, Spain, United Kingdom or Belgium, the european “arabic” numbers are used for the first level of depth","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the ordered bullet list. For the second and third levels, the european alphabets are used with upper and lower case values.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"However for countries speaking arabic, these rules can’t be applied. Indeed, there is no notion of upper and lower case characters in arabic alphabet.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the numbers in use (i.e. the european “arabic” numbers like “1, 2, 3”) are accepted in arabic countries, even if the “true arabic” numbers (like “ ٢ ٣ ١”) are used","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in middle-east arabic countries and for official documents.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus the OUDS ordered bullet list will use “european” numbers for first level, and arabic alphabets for second and third levels.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["       \/\/ 1. Unordered list with bullets","       OUDSBulletList {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 1.1. Item of Unordered list with bullet as tick, a text style","       \/\/ body medium and text bold","       OUDSBulletList(type: .unordered(asset: .tick),","                      textStyle: .bodyMedium,","                      isBold: true)  {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 2. Bare list with 3 items","       OUDSBulletList(type: .bare) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 3. Ordered list with 3 items","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ 3.1. Ordered list with 3 items in first level,","       \/\/ and one item as sub item (second level),","       \/\/ and 2 items as sub item in (third level)","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\") {","               OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1\") {","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.1\")","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.2\")","               }","           }","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }","","       \/\/ Same Bullet list but items in third level with free icon as bullet","       let icon = Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\")","       OUDSBulletList(type: .ordered) {","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1\") {","               OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1\", subListType: .unordered(asset: .icon(icon))) {","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.1\")","                   OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 1.1.2\")","               }","           }","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 2\")","           OUDSBulletList.Item(\"Label 3\")","       }"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-bullet-list","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3,"text":"Orange Compact"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3,"text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_bullet_list_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.0.0 (Figma component design version)"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"1.2.0"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"}]}],"references":{"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSBulletList":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list is a UI element that helps to view in related individual text items grouped together; items usually starting with a number or a bullet."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Bullet list is also known as "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Unordered list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Ordered list","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" and is not an interactive element by default."}],"url":"\/documen